# Sequence Diagram CRUD (Crew, Vendor, Package)

Berikut adalah visualisasi alur Sequence Diagram untuk proses **Create, Read, Update, dan Delete (CRUD)** pada modul Crew, Vendor, dan Package. Diagram ini menggunakan notasi Mermaid.js untuk menggambarkan interaksi antara **Aktor (User/Admin)**, **Interface (Web App/Frontend)**, **Controller (Backend/API)**, dan **Database**.

---

## 1. Create (Tambah Data Baru)
Alur ketika Admin menambahkan data Crew, Vendor, atau Package baru ke dalam sistem.

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Admin
    participant Frontend as Web App (Form input)
    participant Backend as Controller / API
    participant DB as Database

    Admin->>Frontend: Membuka Form Tambah Data
    Frontend-->>Admin: Menampilkan Form Input
    Admin->>Frontend: Mengisi Form & Klik "Simpan"
    Frontend->>Frontend: Validasi Input Client-side
    alt Validasi Gagal
        Frontend-->>Admin: Tampilkan Pesan Error Validasi
    else Validasi Berhasil
        Frontend->>Backend: HTTP POST /api/[resource] (Request Data)
        activate Backend
        Backend->>Backend: Validasi Input Server-side
        alt Validasi Server Gagal
            Backend-->>Frontend: HTTP 422 Unprocessable Entity (Error JSON)
            Frontend-->>Admin: Tampilkan Pesan Error
        else Validasi Server Berhasil
            Backend->>DB: INSERT INTO [crews/vendors/packages]
            activate DB
            DB-->>Backend: Konfirmasi Berhasil (ID Baru)
            deactivate DB
            Backend-->>Frontend: HTTP 201 Created (Success JSON)
            deactivate Backend
            Frontend-->>Admin: Tampilkan Notifikasi Sukses & Redirect ke List Page
        end
    end
```

---

## 2. Read (Membaca & Menampilkan Data)
Alur saat sistem menampilkan daftar data (List) atau detail data spesifik.

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Admin
    participant Frontend as Web App (List/Detail Page)
    participant Backend as Controller / API
    participant DB as Database

    Admin->>Frontend: Membuka Halaman Daftar Data
    Frontend->>Backend: HTTP GET /api/[resource]
    activate Backend
    Backend->>DB: SELECT * FROM [crews/vendors/packages]
    activate DB
    DB-->>Backend: Hasil Query (Data Array)
    deactivate DB
    Backend-->>Frontend: HTTP 200 OK (Data JSON)
    deactivate Backend
    Frontend-->>Admin: Render & Tampilkan Tabel Data

    note over Admin, Frontend: Alur Detail Data (View Detail)
    Admin->>Frontend: Klik Detail Data (ID)
    Frontend->>Backend: HTTP GET /api/[resource]/{id}
    activate Backend
    Backend->>DB: SELECT * FROM [table] WHERE id = {id}
    activate DB
    DB-->>Backend: Single Row Data
    deactivate DB
    Backend-->>Frontend: HTTP 200 OK (Data JSON Object)
    deactivate Backend
    Frontend-->>Admin: Tampilkan Detail Modal/Halaman Detail
```

---

## 3. Update (Mengubah Data)
Alur ketika Admin memperbarui data yang sudah ada di database.

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Admin
    participant Frontend as Web App (Edit Form)
    participant Backend as Controller / API
    participant DB as Database

    Admin->>Frontend: Klik Tombol "Edit" Data (ID)
    Frontend->>Backend: HTTP GET /api/[resource]/{id}/edit
    activate Backend
    Backend->>DB: SELECT * FROM [table] WHERE id = {id}
    activate DB
    DB-->>Backend: Data Saat Ini
    deactivate DB
    Backend-->>Frontend: HTTP 200 OK (Data JSON)
    deactivate Backend
    Frontend-->>Admin: Tampilkan Form Edit dengan Data Terisi

    Admin->>Frontend: Mengubah Data & Klik "Simpan Perubahan"
    Frontend->>Frontend: Validasi Input Client-side
    alt Validasi Gagal
        Frontend-->>Admin: Tampilkan Pesan Error Validasi
    else Validasi Berhasil
        Frontend->>Backend: HTTP PUT/PATCH /api/[resource]/{id} (Request Data)
        activate Backend
        Backend->>Backend: Validasi Input Server-side
        alt Validasi Server Gagal
            Backend-->>Frontend: HTTP 422 Unprocessable Entity
            Frontend-->>Admin: Tampilkan Pesan Error
        else Validasi Server Berhasil
            Backend->>DB: UPDATE [table] SET ... WHERE id = {id}
            activate DB
            DB-->>Backend: Konfirmasi Update Berhasil
            deactivate DB
            Backend-->>Frontend: HTTP 200 OK (Success JSON)
            deactivate Backend
            Frontend-->>Admin: Tampilkan Notifikasi Sukses & Refresh/Redirect Halaman
        end
    end
```

