## 4. Delete (Menghapus Data)
Alur ketika Admin menghapus data secara permanen atau soft delete.

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Admin
    participant Frontend as Web App (List Page)
    participant Backend as Controller / API
    participant DB as Database

    Admin->>Frontend: Klik Tombol "Hapus" pada Data Tertentu
    Frontend-->>Admin: Tampilkan Dialog Konfirmasi ("Yakin ingin menghapus?")
    alt Admin membatalkan (Cancel)
        Admin->>Frontend: Klik "Batal"
        Frontend-->>Admin: Tutup Dialog (Data tidak dihapus)
    else Admin menyetujui (Confirm)
        Admin->>Frontend: Klik "Ya, Hapus"
        Frontend->>Backend: HTTP DELETE /api/[resource]/{id}
        activate Backend
        Backend->>DB: DELETE FROM [table] WHERE id = {id}
        activate DB
        DB-->>Backend: Konfirmasi Data Terhapus
        deactivate DB
        Backend-->>Frontend: HTTP 200 OK (Success JSON)
        deactivate Backend
        Frontend->>Frontend: Hapus Baris Data dari UI DOM
        Frontend-->>Admin: Tampilkan Notifikasi Berhasil Dihapus
    end
```
